{"tid":685260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿政治現況 男子闖法務部丟汽油彈","createTime":"2018-05-31T09:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T09:30:40.000Z","uid":35468,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"469c77b5bf49c3f22fb49e2c88bbfe6819058a87","tid":685260,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:28:48.000Z","msg":"2018-05-31 14:51<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首次上稿 14:51<br />\n更新時間 16:12<br />\n<br />\n〔記者吳政峰／台北報導〕一名54歲的李姓男子今日下午2點多闖入法務部，大喊不滿法務部長邱太三近2年施政，先點燃手上紙袋往一樓櫃檯扔，再朝地面砸破一瓶裝滿汽油的高粱酒瓶，隨即掏出打火機企圖縱火，但未成功，鍾姓保全見狀立即上前制止，阻止悲劇發生，李男隨即被帶回介壽路派出所偵訊。<br />\n<br />\n李男被壓制在地不斷掙扎，稍微冷靜後說出「台灣人就是不會覺醒」、「我是第二個王炳忠」等語，試圖表達對政治的不滿，但無法研判政治傾向。<br />\n<br />\n員警約在5分鐘後到場，但未予以上銬，李男表示要找律師，逕自講手機，情緒看不出波動，亦未大聲咆哮，態度從容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2443444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2443444&d=nmvs43czZi76FBiUJ2hPmb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=adb2a4ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2443444&h=6d6cbdc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2443444</a>"},{"pid":"1cb65cf8b481e381edd3602bada139d459eb4f01","tid":685260,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac042e406b5c9a053c784a6abb482350882c334","tid":685260,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}